00:14:10.217 --> 00:14:12.152 position:19% line:83% align:start
-The big question is...
-[grunts]

00:14:12.186 --> 00:14:13.722 position:13% line:89% align:start
Under these circumstances,

00:14:13.755 --> 00:14:15.523 position:21% line:83% align:start
